keyFacts: This document is an official FBI criminal history record (rap sheet) provided by the New York State Division of Criminal Justice Services on October 6, 2021.
The record is based on fingerprint comparisons and pertains to a single individual, whose identity is fully redacted in the provided text.
The record indicates the subject's DNA is 'NOT IN CODIS' and includes the instruction 'COLLECT DNA'.
The document contains standard legal caveats about the use and currency of the information, stating it is for official use only.
The responding agency's liaison office is located in Clarksburg, West Virginia.
